record.title: VITIATION OF ORDER--H.R. 5140

speaking.paragraph: I ask unanimous consent that the adoption of the motion to proceed to H.R. 5140, the economic stimulus package, not displace any pending measures.

record.chair: Without objection, it is so ordered.

speaking.paragraph: Mr. President, the unanimous consent I just asked for, I would ask that that be withdrawn.

record.chair: Without objection, it is so ordered.
